    "enDesc": "Rabbi Shlomo Adani’s (1567–c.1630) Melekhet Shelomoh commentary on the Mishnah. Authored at the same time as the renowned Tosafot Yom Tov, the Melekhet Shelomoh remained in manuscript form for long after. It was first published in Vilna about two hundred and fifty years after the death of the author.",
